  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "For anyone else coming to this issue, this bug affects nuxt 2 and was introduced in version 4.3.3 with a nuxt 3 fix (https://github.com/algolia/vue-instantsearch/pull/1112). You can resolve it by rolling back to 4.3.2.\r\n\r\nThere's a draft PR to fix the issue here: https://github.com/algolia/vue-instantsearch/pull/1117/files",
