  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "This is how we solved this issue with $nuxt with Vue v2, Nuxt v2.x\r\n\r\n`serverPrefetch() {\r\n  Object.defineProperty(this, '$nuxt', { set: () => {} })\r\n}`",
